YouTube does reserve the
rights to remove the content

104
00:04:26.04 --> 00:04:31.00
with no notification.

105
00:04:31.00 --> 00:04:34.04
Additionally, YouTube does
support copyright enforcement.

106
00:04:34.04 --> 00:04:38.01
So if you find that your content
has been shared illegally,

107
00:04:38.01 --> 00:04:41.05
there are ways to submit
a copyright complaint.

108
00:04:41.05 --> 00:04:43.07
And this allows you to take down content

109
00:04:43.07 --> 00:04:46.07
that you are the rightful
copyright holder on.

110
00:04:46.07 --> 00:04:50.07
But keep in mind, don't
do this frivolously.

111
00:04:50.07 --> 00:04:54.01
If you start to submit copyright
takedown claims on content

112
00:04:54.01 --> 00:04:58.01
that isn't yours, you can
actually face legal problems.

113
00:04:58.01 --> 00:05:01.05
Copyright violation is something
YouTube takes seriously,

114
00:05:01.05 --> 00:05:02.09
as serious as we can say

115
00:05:02.09 --> 00:05:05.08
that they take no responsibilities for it,

116
00:05:05.08 --> 00:05:07.09
