118
00:05:09.08 --> 00:05:11.07
but they will enforce a takedown

119
00:05:11.07 --> 00:05:15.00
and pull down content that
shouldn't be uploaded.

120
00:05:15.00 --> 00:05:17.09
Additionally, for content that others own,

121
00:05:17.09 --> 00:05:19.07
through the content ID system,

122
00:05:19.07 --> 00:05:21.00
they do pay out money

123
00:05:21.00 --> 00:05:23.03
and damages and loyalties

124
00:05:23.03 --> 00:05:27.01
or revenue from the ads
