125
00:05:27.01 --> 00:05:28.07
So YouTube, as it has matured,

126
00:05:28.07 --> 00:05:31.01
has taken copyright more seriously,

127
00:05:31.01 --> 00:05:33.04
and does try to enforce copyright

128
00:05:33.04 --> 00:05:34.07
and create an environment

129
00:05:34.07 --> 00:05:37.05
